{"tid":399423,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我發夢自己6個月之內可以掌握一門外語","createTime":"2017-09-14T02:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T09:58:53.000Z","uid":124439,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"010aab366af909570af8a995e50bc4ca591954d0","tid":399423,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:39:37.000Z","msg":"先以聽同講為主,<br />\n我發現自己真係可以 <br />\n但唔知點去逄合自己既概念<br />\n我要催眠自去實現<br />\n理論上唔應該失敗<br />\n我發覺細聲讀係無效,但要流暢返又非常困難,讀完要記入腦唔易,但運用出黎又好似無可能<br />\n琴晚開始試讀左5句英文,用手提錄低發覺自己個腦真係好識欺騙自己既認知<br />\n過左就唔講啦 只可以講一句說話係逐粒字逐粒漏出黎<br />\n聽成句返更加係怪到不得了<br />\n貌似真係要勤加說話先可以訓練到果肌肉記憶<br />\n有冇咩野心得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS.暫時黎講英文水準幼稚不如,平時講既說話總數唔多於200字<br />\n有專人幫我訓練緊英文每星期大約2小時,報緊兩個工聯會英文課程 每星期一堂"},{"pid":"1e517b7bab0a79f41c5fece4ca0a5c1666a05874","tid":399423,"uid":145027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:09:03.000Z","msg":"小學畢業未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb27a0badc8984ca1c186b374e02e8af423e5a6","tid":399423,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:11:26.000Z","msg":"做乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee42157f2de04bf8c9c2f1f610f41aacf02f8dcd","tid":399423,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:13:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成功學習英文要如何做"},{"pid":"08303cbb2e9a6b0b45f0b7f0bd825652b7cd23f6","tid":399423,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:13:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學畢業未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中五"},{"pid":"f99ca52fad13af86e495b43ca4cfd3025b0003b1","tid":399423,"uid":7744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:13:56.000Z","msg":"1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a